# Render Deployment Configuration

## Environment Variables (set in Render dashboard):
# PYTHONPATH=/opt/render/project/src
# PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1
# API_BASE_URL=https://rag-system-api.onrender.com

## Build Commands:
# API Service: pip install -r requirements.txt
# UI Service: pip install -r requirements.txt

## Start Commands:
# API Service: python -m src.api.main --host 0.0.0.0 --port $PORT
# UI Service: streamlit run ui/app.py --server.port $PORT --server.address 0.0.0.0

## Disk Configuration:
# Mount path: /opt/render/project/src/data
# Size: 1GB (free tier limit)

## Health Check:
# Path: /health
# Timeout: 30s
